Integrity
Systemic Resilience 0.08-0.15      Redundancy + adaptive capacity metrics
Biodiversity        0.05-0.10      Species richness + genetic diversity
Individual          0.05-0.10      Self-determination indices
Autonomy
```

Governance Structure for the PIF:

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Planetary Intelligence Governance Council (PIGC)   │
│  • 21 members serving 7-year terms                  │
│  • 7 from natural sciences                          │
